: {{cite journal |author={{aut|Schieber de Lavarreda, Christa}} |year=2002 |title=La ofrenda de Tak'alik Ab'aj (antes Abaj Takalik) |journal=XV Simposio de Investigaciones Arqueol<U+00F3>gicas en Guatemala, 2001 (edited by J.P. Laporte, H. Escobedo and B. Arroyo) |pages=pp.399-412 |publisher=Museo Nacional de Arqueolog<U+00ED>a y Etnolog<U+00ED>a |location=Guatemala |url=http://www.asociaciontikal.com/pdf/32.01%20-%20Schieber%20-%20en%20PDF.pdf |format=versi<U+00F3>n digital |accessdate=2009/02/01}} {{es icon}}

